{{Expand English|Mycobacterium}}
{{Expand|time=2014-07-02}}

'''分枝杆菌屬'''（'''''Mycobacterium'''''）為[[放线菌门|放线菌门]]下的一個屬，且為分枝桿菌科唯一的屬。为形状不规则的革兰氏阳性杆菌，不能游动，通常抗酸，无气生菌丝和孢子。

该属细菌包括许多已知在[[哺乳類动物|哺乳類动物]]中造成严重疾病的[[病原菌|病原菌]]，包括[[结核杆菌|结核杆菌]]（''Mycobacterium tuberculosis''）和[[麻风杆菌|麻风杆菌]]（''Mycobacterium leprae''）<ref name="Sherris">{{cite book | author = Ryan KJ, Ray CG (editors) | title = Sherris Medical Microbiology | edition = 4th | publisher = McGraw Hill | year = 2004 | isbn = 0-8385-8529-9 }}</ref>。

[[希臘語|希臘語]]中的 ''myco'' 表示「真菌」，意思是說該屬的物種通常在液態培養基的表面，形成類似黴菌的菌落。<ref>James H. Kerr and Terry L. Barrett, "Atypical Mycobacterial Diseases", ''Military Dermatology Textbook'', p. 401.</ref>

{{TOC left}}{{clear}}

==微生物特徵==
[[Image:Mycobacterial_cell_wall_diagram.png|thumb]]：<br>1. 外層脂質<br>2. {{le|mycolic acid}}<br>3. [[多醣|多醣]]（{{le|arabinogalactan}}）<br>4. [[肽聚糖|肽聚糖]]<br>5. [[細胞膜|細胞膜]]<br>6. {{le|lipoarabinomannan}}（LAM）<br>7. {{le|phosphatidylinositol mannoside}}<br>8. 細胞壁骨架]]

本屬物種為好氧型細菌，且為不運動型細菌（[[海洋分枝桿菌|海洋分枝桿菌]]除外，其可以在[[巨噬細胞|巨噬細胞]]內運動），為一種{{le|Acid-fast|Acid-fast|抗酸型細菌}}<ref name=Sherris />。分枝桿菌並不會形成[[内孢子|内孢子]]或[[莢膜|莢膜]]，因此常被認定為[[革蘭氏陰性菌|革蘭氏陰性菌]]。且分枝桿菌在革蘭氏染色上並無法染上[[結晶紫|結晶紫]]，因此無法被歸類於革蘭氏陽性菌或陰性菌。

雖然說本屬不產孢子，但有兩個物種似乎例外，那就是[[海洋分枝桿菌|海洋分枝桿菌]]（''Mycobacterium marinum''）和牛分枝桿菌（''M. bovis''）<ref>Ghosh, Jaydip, Pontus Larsson, Bhupender Singh, B M Fredrik Pettersson, Nurul M Islam, Sailendra Nath Sarkar, Santanu Dasgupta, y Leif A Kirsebom. 2009. "Sporulation in mycobacteria". ''Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America'' 106, no. 26 (Junio 30): 10781-10786. http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19541637 {{Wayback|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19541637 |date=20190515161123 }}</ref>。但進一步的研究引發了爭論。<ref>Traag BA, Driks A, Stragier P, Bitter W, Broussard G, Hatfull G, Chu F, Adams KN, Ramakrishnan L, Losick R.2010. "Do mycobacteria produce endospores?" ''Proc Natl Acad Sci U S A''. 2010 Jan 12;107(2):878-81.</ref>

分枝桿菌的特點就是其細胞壁較其他物種厚，且呈蠟狀疏水性，並含有大量的{{le|分枝菌酸|mycolic acids}}（mycolic acids）。多醣會將分枝菌酸層及肽聚糖層拉在一起，讓細胞壁變得十分堅韌。若可干擾其細胞壁的生物合成途徑，也許可以開發治療[[肺結核|肺結核]]的藥物。<ref name= BhamidiS>{{cite book |author= Bhamidi S|year=2009|chapter=Mycobacterial Cell Wall Arabinogalactan|title=Bacterial Polysaccharides: Current Innovations and Future Trends|publisher=Caister Academic Press|isbn= 978-1-904455-45-5}}</ref>

== 物種 ==
[[Image:Mycobacterium_phylogenetic_tree.png|thumb]]

表型测试可用于识别和区分不同的分枝杆菌物种和菌株。在以前的系统中，分枝杆菌根据它们的外观和生长速度进行分组的。然而，这些是近祖共性（symplesiomorphies）的，并且最近的分类基于[[支序分类学|支序分类学]]（cladistics）进行的。

===慢速生長菌===

====结核分枝杆菌复合群<ref name="#1">https://www.termonline.cn/search?k=Mycobacterium%20tuberculosis%20complex&r=</ref> （''Mycobacterium tuberculosis'' complex）====
* {{tsl|en|Mycobacterium tuberculosis complex||''Mycobacterium tuberculosis'' complex}} (MTBC) members are causative agents of human and animal tuberculosis. Species in this complex include:
*: [[結核桿菌|結核桿菌]]（ ''Mycobacterium tuberculosis''），肺结核分枝杆菌，[[肺結核|肺結核]]的主要致病菌。
*: [[牛分枝杆菌|牛分枝杆菌]] ''Mycobacterium bovis''
*: [[卡介苗|卡介苗]] ''Mycobacterium bovis BCG''
*: [[非洲分支杆菌|非洲分支杆菌]] ''Mycobacterium africanum''
*: [[卡氏分枝杆菌|卡氏分枝杆菌]] ''Mycobacterium canetti''
*: [[羊分枝杆菌|羊分枝杆菌]] ''Mycobacterium caprae''
*: [[田鼠分枝杆菌|田鼠分枝杆菌]] ''Mycobacterium microti''
*: [[海豹分枝杆菌|海豹分枝杆菌]] ''Mycobacterium pinnipedii''，鳍脚亚目动物分枝杆菌

====鸟分枝杆菌复合群<ref name="#1"/><ref>https://terms.naer.edu.tw/search/?q=Mycobacterium+avium+complex&field=ti&op=AND&group=&num=10</ref> （''Mycobacterium avium'' complex）====
* {{tsl|en|Mycobacterium avium complex||''Mycobacterium avium'' complex (MAC)}} is a group of species that, in a disseminated infection but not lung infection, used to be a significant cause of death in [[艾滋病|AIDS]] patients. The species ''M. indicus pranii''  appears to be basal in this complex.<ref name=Rahman2014>Rahman SA, Singh Y, Kohli S, Ahmad J, Ehtesham NZ, Tyagi AK, Hasnain SE (2014) Comparative analyses of nonpathogenic, opportunistic, and totally pathogenic ''Mycobacteria'' reveal genomic and biochemical variabilities and highlight the survival attributes of ''Mycobacterium tuberculosis''. MBio 5(6). pii: e02020-14. doi: 10.1128/mBio.02020-14</ref>Species in this complex include:
*: ''{{tsl|en|Mycobacterium avium avium||M. avium}}''
*: 鸟分枝杆菌类结核亚种 ''{{tsl|en|Mycobacterium avium paratuberculosis||M. avium paratuberculosis}}'', which has been implicated in [[克隆氏症|Crohn's disease]] in humans and is the causative agent of {{tsl|en|Johne's disease||Johne's disease}} in [[家牛|cattle]] and [[綿羊|sheep]]
*: ''{{tsl|en|Mycobacterium avium silvaticum||M. avium silvaticum}}''
*: ''{{tsl|en|Mycobacterium avium hominissuis||M. avium "hominissuis"}}''
*: [[哥伦比亚分枝杆菌|哥伦比亚分枝杆菌]] ''{{tsl|en|Mycobacterium colombiense||M. colombiense}}''
*: ''{{tsl|en|Mycobacterium indicus pranii||M. indicus pranii}}''

